		synchronizedReader.setDelegate(new ExcelItemReader());
		synchronizedReader.afterPropertiesSet();
		return synchronizedReader;
	}

You can find more details about this reader in the [Item readers and writers decorators](https://docs.spring.io/spring-batch/4.2.x/reference/html/readersAndWriters.html#synchronizedItemStreamReader) section.

