          group: &#39;y&#39;

, or it is possible to use [host_vars](https://docs.ansible.com/ansible/latest/user_guide/intro_inventory.html#assigning-a-variable-to-one-machine-host-variables)

    $ tree host_vars
    host_vars
     XXX
